"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-31-canada-fail-bid-overturn-six-point-deduction-olympic-football\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS,\\u00a0France (AFP)- Canada's six-point deduction over a spying scandal at the women's Olympic football has been upheld after an appeal to the Court of Arbitration for Sport failed on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998606726530047, \"rank\": 0.0001355075695827407, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Swiss-based body was asked to review the punishment handed down by world football's governing body FIFA which has left the reigning Olympic champions in danger of a group-stage exit at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9999999982167083, \"rank\": 1.139625645710869e-09, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada have won both of their matches so far, against New Zealand and France, but the penalty means they have zero points with only one group game remaining.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 403, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999919192161075, \"rank\": 7.509147811243639e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\"